Description: Provides 'ggplot2' extensions to construct glyph-maps for visualizing seasonality in spatiotemporal data. See the Journal of Statistical Software reference: <doi:10.18637/jss.v110.i07>. The manuscript for this package is currently under preparation and can be found on GitHub at <https://github.com/maliny12/paper-sugarglider>. 
